                         4  ;                  SAMPLE 6
                         5  ;      THIS IS A TWELVE HOUR CLOCK PRO
       GRAM
                         6  ;      THE ACCURACY IS DEPENDENT UPON 
       THE MPU CLOCK
                         7  ;      FREQUENCY AND THE TIMING LOOP A
       T START.
                         8  ;      CHANGING THE VALUE AT 0005/6 BY
       HEX 100
                         9  ;      CHANGES THE ACCURACY APPROXIMAT
       ELY 1 SEC/MIN.
                        10  ;      HOURS.MINUTE.SECOND RMB 0001/2/
       3 ARE LOADED
                        11  ;      WITH THE STARTING TIME. THE FIR
       ST DISPLAY
                        12  ;      IS ONE SECOND AFTER START OF TH
       E PROGRAM.
                        13  ;      SECONDS WILL BE CONTENT OF SECO
       ND RMB +1.
                        14  ;      USES MONITOR SUBROUTINES REDIS,
       DISPLAY.
                        15  ;      NOTE:START THE PROGRAM AT 0004.
                        16  
